cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: research-to-paper
abstract: >-
  A fully self-contained Claude Code / Codex skill that takes a research idea to a
  submission-ready manuscript: scope the direction, build a DOI-verified literature
  library (with biology resource search across NCBI / UniProt / RCSB PDB / AlphaFold /
  Europe PMC), draft with evidence-matched hedging, run multi-agent adversarial review,
  de-AI the prose, and render LaTeX / Word / PDF — depending on no other skill.
type: software
